quran[31]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,43,"Wọn yóò wí pé: “Àwa kò sí nínú àwọn olùkírun ni."
  74,44,"Àwa kò sì sí nínú àwọn tó ń bọ́ àwọn mẹ̀kúnnù."
  74,45,"Àwa sì máa ń sọ ìsọkúsọ pẹ̀lú àwọn onísọkúsọ."
  75,40,"Ǹjẹ́ Ẹni tí Ó ṣe ìyẹn kò níí ní agbára láti jí àwọn òkú dìde bí?"
  77,31,"Kì í ṣe ibòji tútù. Kò sì níí rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀ nínú ìjòfòfò Iná."
  77,32,"Dájúdájú (Iná náà) yóò máa ju ẹ̀tapàrà (rẹ̀ sókè tó máa dà) bí pẹ̀tẹ́ẹ̀sì."
  77,33,"(Ó máa dà) bí àwọn ràkúnmí aláwọ̀ omi ọsàn."
  78,28,"Wọ́n sì pe àwọn āyah Wa ní irọ́ gan-an."
  78,29,"Gbogbo n̄ǹkan sì ni A ti ṣe àkọsílẹ̀ rẹ̀ sínú Tírà kan."
  78,30,"Nítorí náà, ẹ tọ́ (ìyà) wò. A ò sì níí ṣe àlékún kan fún yín bí kò ṣe ìyà."
  79,22,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó kẹ̀yìn sí i. Ó sì ń ṣiṣẹ́ (takò ó)."
  79,23,"Ó kó (àwọn ènìyàn) jọ, ó sì ké gbàjarì."
  79,24,"Ó sì wí pé: “Èmi ni olúwa yín, ẹni gíga jùlọ.”"
  80,19,"Nínú àtọ̀ l’Ó ti ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀. Ó sì pèbùbù (ẹ̀yà-ara) rẹ̀."
  80,20,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó ṣe ọ̀nà àtiwáyé ní ìrọ̀rùn fún un."
  80,21,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó máa pa á. Ó sì máa fi sínú sàréè."
  81,16,"(ìyẹn) àwọn ìràwọ̀ tó ń rìn lọ rìn bọ̀, tó ń wọ̀ọ̀kùn sí ibùwọ̀ wọn."
  81,17,"Mo tún fi alẹ́ nígbà tí ó bá lọ búra.1 {1}",footnotes:1:Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn: Mo tún fi alẹ́ nígbà tí ó bá wọlé búra.
  81,18,"Mo tún fi òwúrọ̀ nígbà tí ó bá mọ́lẹ̀ búra."
  82,10,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹ̀ṣọ́ sì wà ní ọ̀dọ̀ yín."
  82,11,"(Wọ́n jẹ́) alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé, òǹkọ̀wé-iṣẹ́ ẹ̀dá."
  82,12,"Wọ́n mọ ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  83,7,"Ní ti òdodo dájúdájú ìwé iṣẹ́ àwọn ẹni burúkú (tó ń dín òṣùwọ̀n kù) kúkú máa wà nínú Sijjīn."
  83,8,"Kí sì l’ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Sijjīn!"
  83,9,"Ìwé tí wọ́n ti kọ iṣẹ́ aburú ẹ̀dá sínú rẹ̀ (tí wọ́n sì fi pamọ́ sínú ilẹ̀ keje ni Sijjīn)."
  84,4,"ó máa ju ohun tí ó wà nínú rẹ̀ síta, ó sì máa pa sófo"
  84,5,"- ó gbọ́, ó sì tẹ̀lé àṣẹ Olúwa rẹ̀ ni. Ó sì di dandan fún un láti ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀ - (ní ọjọ́ yẹn ni ẹ̀dá máa rí iṣẹ́ ọwọ́ rẹ̀)"
  84,6,"Ìwọ ènìyàn dájúdájú ìwọ ń ṣe iṣẹ́ kárakára ní iṣẹ́ àṣepàdé Olúwa rẹ. O sì máa mú un pàdé Rẹ̀."
  85,1,"(Allāhu) fi sánmọ̀ tí àwọn ibùsọ̀ (òòrùn, òṣùpá àti àwọn ìràwọ̀) wà nínú rẹ̀ búra."
  85,2,"Ó tún fi ọjọ́ tí wọ́n ṣe ní àdéhùn (ìyẹn Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde) búra."
  85,3,"Ó tún fi olùjẹ́rìí àti ohun tó jẹ́rìí sí búra."